{"tid":524084,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【腳壞死變黑】德州女食生蠔感染弧菌死","createTime":"2018-01-09T08:25:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-09T10:19:25.000Z","uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"201f4f4cd828c61fb6029bc9ca9327e28e806958","tid":524084,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T08:25:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180109/large/1515469104_4466.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180109%2Flarge%2F1515469104_4466.jpg&h=cef1f7a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國德州一位中年婦女在捉蟹及進食生蠔後感染弧菌病（Vibriosis），她在病床上博鬥21日，雙腳腐爛發黑，終不敵病魔慘死。<br />\n<br />\n55歲的勒布朗（Jeanette LeBlanc）去年到路易斯安那州探望親友，期間曾捉蟹及進食朋友在一個市場買的生蠔。根據美國疾病管制與預防中心，人類可經進食生或未徹底煮熟的貝類，特別是生蠔而感染弧菌，另外傷口接觸到鹹淡水，也有機會感染弧菌，而勒布朗當天兩樣都做齊。<br />\n<br />\n朋友憶述，當日與勒布朗一同進食了20多隻生蠔。勒布朗後來感到不適，約36小時後腳上出疹，勒布朗的同性伴侶還以為她有過敏反應。勒布朗的情況在48個小時內惡化，須送院治理，醫生確診她感染弧菌，期間她的腿部肌肉更壞死變黑。與病魔博鬥21日，勒布朗延至去年10月15日不治。<br />\n<br />\n研究弧菌的微生物學家加布里埃爾（Gabrielle Barbarite）表示，弧菌其實不是食肉菌，因為人一旦接觸到弧菌，它也不會分解皮膚。她續道：「你要早有傷口，或吃掉生的受污染海鮮，或飲下很多受污染的水，它才能進入你的血管。」<br />\n<br />\n勒布朗的同性伴侶慨嘆：「假如我們知道風險這麼高，我想她會不吃生蠔。」<br />\n<br />\n美國《今日美國報》/英國《每日郵報》  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180109/57684009\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180109%2F57684009&d=U%2BkWzTdhjVf0XVIsnGw%2BvwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=81cac5bd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180109%2F57684009&h=e267e83c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180109/57684009</a>"},{"pid":"a2a2a31bb31c188ea4b3764360d104d31db6e7e1","tid":524084,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T08:32:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1efd09c86a117d2e2963310aeb888d7b167ea99","tid":524084,"uid":75969,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a2a2a31bb31c188ea4b3764360d104d31db6e7e1","tid":524084,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T08:32:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T08:34:21.000Z","msg":"之前都好鍾意食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f98bc748ae3cd142021f949c7944682bde1eecd1","tid":524084,"uid":123711,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T08:34:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"73098e1ab1cd6240cbccefec7512000e3442e3de","tid":524084,"uid":60057,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T09:08:47.000Z","msg":"勒布朗食生蠔感染弧菌死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba63712a727d655da81cec19ee7e8f97130b8bf7","tid":524084,"uid":40588,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T09:15:23.000Z","msg":"黑到仲以為係d泥"},{"pid":"425831f4a320c3070df115ede38d64b1c0ecb2d5","tid":524084,"uid":156618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T09:33:26.000Z","msg":"D 強國人食返而冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c264838203b99c9d2f49a4a342db63823b5b5ad","tid":524084,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T09:59:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/mo6-HuLUHpI/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2Fmo6-HuLUHpI%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=22c9e028&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢用幻術詐死呃保險咋話?"},{"pid":"035856a08e368c9e7e5949d4ceb63083f97eecce","tid":524084,"uid":11962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"425831f4a320c3070df115ede38d64b1c0ecb2d5","tid":524084,"uid":156618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,